             was indicted for <rs id="t18020428-67-off363" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18020428-67-off363" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18020428-67-off363" type="offenceSubcategory" value="theftFromPlace"></interp>
               feloniously stealing, on the <rs id="t18020428-67-cd364" type="crimeDate">25th of April</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18020428-67-off363 t18020428-67-cd364"></join>, a pair of sheets, value 5s. the property of 
                     
                        <persName id="t18020428-67-victim546" type="victimName">
                           Benjamin 
                           Steel
                        <interp inst="t18020428-67-victim546" type="surname" value="Steel"></interp>
